quran[14]{c,v,t,f}:
  106,1,"Kubera akamenyero k’Abakurayishi (mu mujyi wabo),",""
  106,2,"No kubera amasezerano yabo arebana n’ingendo (z’ubucuruzi) zo mu gihe cy’ubukonje no mu cy’impeshyi (batekanye),",""
  106,3,"Ngaho nibagaragire (Allah) Nyagasani nyir’iyi ngoro (Al Ka’abat),",""
  106,4,"(We) wabagaburiye mu gihe cy’amapfa, ndetse akanabaha umutekano mu gihe cy’ubwoba.",""
  107,1,"Ese wamenye uhinyura umunsi w’ibihembo?",""
  107,2,"Uwo ni wa wundi uhutaza imfubyi,",""
  107,3,"Ntanashishikarize (abandi) kugaburira abakene,",""
  107,4,"Bityo, ibihano bikomeye biri ku basenga,",""
  107,5,"Ba bandi birengagiza iswala zabo (ntibazikorere ku bihe byazo byagenwe)",""
  107,6,"Ba bandi bakora ibyiza bagamije kwiyerekana,",""
  107,7,"Kandi bakanga (gutiza) ibikoresho byo mu rugo (ababikeneye).",""
  108,1,"Mu by’ukuri (yewe Muhamadi) twaguhaye ibyiza byinshi (birimo n’umugezi wo mu Ijuru witwa Kawthar).",""
  108,2,"Bityo, ujye usali unatange ibitambo kubera Nyagasani wawe.",""
  108,3,"Mu by’ukuri ukwanga ni we nyakamwe (ntazigera abona ibyiza haba ku isi ndetse no ku mperuka).",""
